    <h1>Impressions (SEO)</h1>
    <p class="description">The count of how many times your URL appeared in a Google search result. Measured in <strong>Google Search Console</strong>, impressions are your search visibility metric — they show how often Google showed your pages, regardless of whether anyone clicked.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
